{"tid":2151423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Like Japan TV訪問了一位去年走在前線的日本攝影師。","createTime":"2020-08-11T11:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T11:43:38.000Z","uid":217430,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf191735d48f930aa08a034a48984f08df8c2be","tid":2151423,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:24:56.000Z","msg":"Like Japan TV訪問了一位去年走在前線的日本攝影師，她叫KISEKI MICHIKO。<br />\nMICHIKO小時候曾住過香港。17年，她亦來過香港，拍攝了很多街頭、展現香港生活百態的照片。<br />\n<br />\n香港人的生命力、笑容、積極向上的態度，讓一個問題在她腦海中一直揮之不去：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">「他們為什麼這麼有活力？」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n為了找到答案，MICHIKO在去年7月，決定再次回到香港，停留半年，製作攝影作品。<br />\n<br />\n去年8月尾，手足在MICHIKO面前被黑警拘捕。其過程震撼了她。她亦決定要繼續走上前線，拍攝和紀錄著香港的示威活動。<br />\n<br />\n拍了一張又一張前線抗爭相片。<br />\n<br />\n去年十二月，MICHIKO在日本舉辦了一場關於反送中運動的攝影展。讓更多日本人知道香港到底在發生什麼事，更多在日本媒體中，無法看到的抗爭畫面。<br />\n<br />\n一位日本攝影師，不自覺地打通日本國際戰線。<br />\n把香港人和日本人的心連結在一起，讓更多日本人關注、支持香港的抗爭運動。<br />\n<br />\n多謝你，MICHIKO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\">大家不妨follow一下MICHIKO的IG/Twitter。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/kisekimichiko?igshid=1tkzy9m4j35xf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fkisekimichiko%3Figshid%3D1tkzy9m4j35xf&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=87925891\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/kisekimichiko?igshid=1tkzy9m4j35xf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kisekimichiko?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkisekimichiko%3Fs%3D21&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=82585567\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kisekimichiko?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\">她的個人網站有香港抗爭的攝影集售賣</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kisekimichiko.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kisekimichiko.com&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=adc8bda0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kisekimichiko.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\">Like Japan TV訪問</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QvgHrooWlOs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQvgHrooWlOs&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=a013ee5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QvgHrooWlOs</a>"},{"pid":"9282ffc8337d3ebf414403915793025677ece769","tid":2151423,"uid":217430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成個訪問都好精彩，多謝你，Like Japan TV"},{"pid":"04a12ab69cbc97b5beb02566fac9dca51c36364c","tid":2151423,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:29:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f41609129dd9c19f005a40806589fae3356af3c","tid":2151423,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9c1a3b91319586e365f3e002781af2c3006e0d7","tid":2151423,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8511c6471c8359fffe765f9a835f6fd8d044905","tid":2151423,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:30:30.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9520bab5ca05cdac3169e1274968b801e2834e8","tid":2151423,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:35:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b7f34428d8e21a4dd5586be7b504ebd7faf9465","tid":2151423,"uid":67006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4247e